title: Apply for a Bevin Boys veterans badge

heading_context: Apply for a Bevin Boys veterans badge
chunks.html_content: You can get a Bevin Boys veterans badge if you worked in the coal mines under the Bevin Boys scheme - widows of Bevin Boys may also be eligible.
chunks.plain_content:
Apply for a Bevin Boys veterans badge
You can get a Bevin Boys veterans badge if you worked in the coal mines under the Bevin Boys scheme - widows of Bevin Boys may also be eligible.

heading_context: Apply for a Bevin Boys veterans badge
chunks.html_content:
You’ll get a badge if:

  • you worked in the mines under the Bevin Boys scheme between 1943 and 1948
  • you’re the widow of a Bevin Boy who died on or after 20 June 2007
chunks.plain_content:
Apply for a Bevin Boys veterans badge
Eligibility
You’ll get a badge if:

  you worked in the mines under the Bevin Boys scheme between 1943 and 1948
  you’re the widow of a Bevin Boy who died on or after 20 June 2007

heading_context: Apply for a Bevin Boys veterans badge
chunks.html_content: All Bevin Boys are eligible - it does not matter if you volunteered or were a ‘ballotee’ (conscript).
chunks.plain_content:
Apply for a Bevin Boys veterans badge
Eligibility
All Bevin Boys are eligible - it does not matter if you volunteered or were a ‘ballotee’ (conscript).

heading_context: Apply for a Bevin Boys veterans badge
chunks.html_content:
There is no fee for applying for a veterans badge.

Fill in a Bevin Boys veterans badge application and send it by email or post to the Coal Liabilities Unit.

Contact the Coal Liabilities Unit if you need help completing the form.
chunks.plain_content:
Apply for a Bevin Boys veterans badge
How to apply
There is no fee for applying for a veterans badge.
Fill in a Bevin Boys veterans badge application and send it by email or post to the Coal Liabilities Unit.
Contact the Coal Liabilities Unit if you need help completing the form.
